#

Truffle Infused Potato Gnocchi

25 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

QuickEasyComfort Food

Description

Deliciously soft gnocchi infused with rich truffle flavor, served simply with butter and herbs.

Ingredients

  • potato gnocchi: 1 package (16 oz)
  • truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • butter: 3 tablespoons
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup (chopped)
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
